# Linux + NGINX HTML Deployment

This project demonstrates hosting a static HTML webpage using **NGINX on Linux**.

## ðŸ”§ Technologies Used
- Linux (Ubuntu)
- NGINX Web Server
- HTML
- Basic Networking (Ports, HTTP)

## ðŸš€ Steps Performed
1. Installed NGINX on Linux server
2. Created a custom HTML webpage
3. Configured NGINX server block
4. Deployed webpage on port 80
5. Verified access using browser

